content:
Track Repair and Maintenance Costs for Assets Using Quotes

Use the new Asset field on a Quote Action record to track the estimated cost of products or services you offer to a customer. For example, track the cost of repairing a faulty part and share the quote with the customer to get a confirmation before a service agent starts the work.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Automotive is enabled.

Who: Users must have Create access on Quote, Quote Action, and Asset objects.
title: Track Asset Maintenance Costs with Quotes
